.svg|24px|r\u00f3men]]\t|| U+E018\t|| TENGWAR LETTER ROOMEN\n|-\n| arda\t|| [[Image:Tengwa arda.svg|24px|arda]]\t|| U+E019\t|| TENGWAR LETTER ARDA\n|-\n| lamb\u00eb\t|| [[Image:Tengwa lambe.svg|24px|lamb\u00eb]]\t|| U+E01A\t|| TENGWAR LETTER LAMBE\n|-\n| alda\t|| [[Image:Tengwa alda.svg|24px|alda]]\t|| U+E01B\t|| TENGWAR LETTER ALDA\n|-\n| silm\u00eb\t|| [[Image:Tengwa silme.svg|24px|silm\u00eb]]\t|| U+E01C\t|| TENGWAR LETTER SILME\n|-\n| silm\u00eb nuquerna\t|| [[Image:Tengwa silme nuquerna.svg|24px|silm\u00eb nuquerna]]\t|| U+E01D\t|| TENGWAR LETTER SILME NUQUERNA\n|-\n| ess\u00eb / \u00e1re/\u00e1ze\t|| [[Image:Tengwa esse.svg|24px|ess\u00eb / \u00e1re/\u00e1ze]]\t|| U+E01E\t|| TENGWAR LETTER AARE (aaze, esse)\n|-\n| ess\u00eb nuquerna / \u00e1re/\u00e1ze nuquerna\t|| [[Image:Tengwa esse nuquerna.svg|24px|ess\u00eb nuquerna / \u00e1re/\u00e1ze nuquerna]]\t|| U+E01F\t|| TENGWAR LETTER AARE NUQUERNA (aaze n., esse n.)\n|-\n| hyarmen\t|| [[Image:Tengwa hyarmen.svg|24px|hyarmen]]\t|| U+E020\t|| TENGWAR LETTER HYARMEN\n|-\n| hwesta sindarinwa\t|| [[Image:Tengwa hwesta sindarinwa.svg|24px|hwesta sindarinwa]]\t|| U+E021\t|| TENGWAR LETTER HWESTA SINDARINWA\n|-\n| yanta\t|| [[Image:Tengwa yanta.svg|24px|yanta]]\t|| U+E022\t|| TENGWAR LETTER YANTA\n|-\n| \u00far\u00eb\t|| [[Image:Tengwa \u00fare.svg|24px|\u00far\u00eb]]\t|| U+E023\t|| TENGWAR LETTER UURE\n|-\n| halla\t|| [[Image:Tengwa halla.gif|24px|halla]]\t|| U+E024\t|| TENGWAR LETTER HALLA\n|-\n| telco\t|| [[Image:Tengwa telco.svg|24px|telco]]\t|| U+E025\t|| TENGWAR LETTER SHORT CARRIER\n|-\n| \u00e1ra\t|| [[Image:Tengwa \u00e1ra.svg|24px|\u00e1ra]]\t|| U+E026\t|| TENGWAR LETTER LONG CARRIER\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Tengwar ligatures and extended letters CSUR encoding\n! Name\t!! Image\t!! CSUR\t|| Designation annotation\n|-\n| \t|| \t|| U+E027\t|| TENGWAR LETTER ANNA SINDARINWA\n|-\n| \t|| \t|| U+E028\t|| TENGWAR LETTER EXTENDED THUULE\n|-\n| \t|| \t|| U+E029\t|| TENGWAR LETTER EXTENDED FORMEN\n|-\n| \t|| \t